@NODE req "System Requirements"
@{BG SHINE}
    system requirements
@{BG BACK}
To play BlocksXL you will require an Amiga with the following specification:

OS 2.0 or higher
1.5 Mb of ram
68020 CPU or higher processor recommended for faster loading and smoother game play.

@ENDNODE

